{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"盖被的人啊！"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"你应当起来，你应当警告，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"你应当颂扬你的主宰，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"你应当洗涤你的衣服，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"你应当远离污秽，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"你不要施恩而求厚报，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"你应当为你的主而坚忍。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"当号角被吹向的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"在那时，将有一个艰难的日子。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"那个日子对不信道的人们，是不容易渡过的。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"你让我独自处治我所创造的那个人吧！"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"我赏赐他丰富的财产，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"和在跟前的子嗣，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"我提高了他的声望，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"而他还企望我再多加赏赐。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"绝不然！他确实是反对我的迹象的，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"我将使他遭受苦难。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"他碓已思考，确已计划。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"但无论他怎样计划，他是被弃绝的。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"无论他怎样计划，他终是被弃绝的。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"他看一看，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"然后皱眉蹙额，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"然后高傲地转过身去，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"而且说：“这只是传习的魔术，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"这只是凡人的言辞。”"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"我将使他堕入火狱，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"你怎能知道火狱是什么？"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"它不让任何物存在，不许任何物留下，"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"它烧灼肌肤。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"管理它的，共计十九名。"},{"SurahNumber":74,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"我只将管理火狱的造成天使，我只以他们的数目，考验不信道的人们，以便曾受天经的人们认清，而信道的人们更加笃信；以免曾受天经的人们和信道的人们怀疑；以便心中有病者和不信道者说：安拉设这个譬喻做什么？安拉这样使他所意欲的人误入迷途，使他所意欲的人遵循正路。只有你的主，能知道他的军队，这只是人类的教训。"}]}